    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Enhanced Delta-Sigma Analog-to-Digital Converter module (EDSADC) provides a series of analog input channels connected to on-chip modulators using the Delta/Sigma (DS) conversion principle"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Digital input channels accept data streams from external modulators. The on-chip demodulator channels convert these inputs to discrete digital values"
    },
